<BR>
Okay, this is what i did:<BR>
<BR>
First, i went from HH to Perma for about 2 hours (stayed in qeynos for an hour) Then i met my old friend Forscorcere my god! he's lvl 32 now.  So then i asked him to help me get the skin and we started to clean perma. After an hour we still haven't found any skins and he had to log.<BR>
The next i log on it was hell still, only a lvl 51 rake in perma (i guess he's lvl 60 now, i did this quest when the summer just started) and he would help me. UGH!<BR>
So i just sat there and watch ppl killing IG in everfrost.  The next day i go on, i asked loads of ppl and some of them agreed to help. But 2 hours nothing.<BR>
Then i saw that guy, a lvl 7 magician with a lvl 4ty somethin cleric and a monk.  <BR>
They were coming for the skin too. So i asked the if they could help me 2 but then suddenly, a guy shouted. "Frost GS at king room." I ran sooo fast to king room and looted the corpse of an elite guard. and i gated back to BB.<BR>
<BR>
Well, then i hanged around Qeynos for about 2 hours, chatting with my guild, then i asked someone to teleport me to sro. I went to oasis and i teamed up with my friend. We killed a few orcs and i decided it's time to do the final bit of the quest (oh forgot to mention that when i was lvl 9 i went to sis camp in lfay and a guy killed the faerie guards and gave me the twice-woven cloak)<BR>
I asked someone to teleport me to lavastorm mountain and k, i am there in sol A. <BR>
<BR>
It's not a very good memory I TELL U. tHE FIRE GOBLIN SKIN JUST CAN'T DROP OFF.  Then i met that really nice in gatekeepers of norrath. he helped me to get fire goblin skin for about 3 hours. but when the fire skin was dropped and train came. and u knmow... everything was washed away<BR>
<BR>
Then i asked him to log on the next day and help me again he said yes.  But when i log on again at about 11 o'clock i saw another VERY NICE GUY in a guild i forgot what it was. anyway he was japanese a lvl 4ty somethin bard and he managed to get me killed for about 10 times and i lost a lvl. but the point is not here, the point is that he got me the skin after 1 hour of camping fire goblins in bar room. i thanked him and gated back to lavastorm.<BR>
<BR>
I was very nervous when i gave the things to joyce, i didn't know if i would succeed or not so i slowly placed the items there and GIVE! YES U GAINED EXPERIANCE AND A ROBE APPEARED IN MY INVENTORY!!!!!!!!!!!! what a wonderful feeling u started to tell everyone, in ur guild, friends, etc. then i asked someone to tp me to wc and i ran to freeport. u realize that ppl r starting to inspect u and especially a guy in Assassins of Hindmer, he asked me how i ghot it just right when i got it.<BR>
